Nutrition Classes are offered every first (1st) and third (3rd) Saturday at 9:30am at the Oak Park Community Center, located at 3415 Martin Luther King, Jr. Blvd. Sacramento, CA 95817. Fitness Classes are offered every second (2nd) Saturday at the same schedule and location.
    </p>
    
